                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎最新动态#</a>【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%891%E4%B8%87%E5%A4%9A%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E9%98%9F%E5%91%98%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%23&amp;from=default">#全国有1万多医疗队员支援湖北#</a>】在湖北疫情防控发布会上，湖北副省长杨云彦表示，截至2月5日，全国共有107支医疗队，10596名医疗队员支援湖北省医疗救治工作。对此，湖北人民表示深深的感谢。<a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=人民日报">@人民日报</a> <a suda-uatrack="key=tblog_card&amp;value=click_title:4469084442279903:1042163-video:1042163%3A4469081005555754:page_100206_home:2286908003:4469084442279903:2286908003" title="人民日报的微博视频" href="http://t.cn/A6P1LKhM" alt="http://t.cn/A6P1LKhM" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_video">L</i>人民日报的微博视频</a> ​​​​                                            </div>
